    {
      "id": "RO894Vkuy8OtWg4EFfJb0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5746.7017177382,
      "y": 7249.8210876333615,
      "width": 4806.490936533147,
      "height": 548.967388181212,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b02",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1546555473,
      "version": 1553,
      "versionNonce": 849047615,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783319148125,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Adaptive Bitrate Streaming (Simple Notes)\n- A video is split into many small segments (chunks).\n- Multiple versions of each segment are created (e.g., 1080p, 720p, 480p).\n- During upload, a manifest file is created.\n- The manifest file acts like an index/map that contains links to all video segments and their available qualities.",
      "fontSize": 87.83478210899393,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Adaptive Bitrate Streaming (Simple Notes)\n- A video is split into many small segments (chunks).\n- Multiple versions of each segment are created (e.g., 1080p, 720p, 480p).\n- During upload, a manifest file is created.\n- The manifest file acts like an index/map that contains links to all video segments and their available qualities.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MZB4dwF6n5plH-k15369T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5088.465210112235,
      "y": 9193.70996200158,
      "width": 1528.2606972141677,
      "height": 2263.138675644896,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b03",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1995899889,
      "version": 1198,
      "versionNonce": 1668525105,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783319163000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User Uploads Video\n    ↓\nS3 Stores Original Video\n    ↓\nS3 Event Notification\n    ↓\nVideo Processing Service\n    ↓\nCreate Multiple Qualities\n(1080p, 720p, 480p)\n    ↓\nSplit Each Quality into Segments\n    ↓\nGenerate Manifest File\n    ↓\nStore Segments + Manifest in S3\n    ↓\nUpdate VideoMetadata\n(with Manifest URL)",
      "fontSize": 95.29004950083771,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User Uploads Video\n    ↓\nS3 Stores Original Video\n    ↓\nS3 Event Notification\n    ↓\nVideo Processing Service\n    ↓\nCreate Multiple Qualities\n(1080p, 720p, 480p)\n    ↓\nSplit Each Quality into Segments\n    ↓\nGenerate Manifest File\n    ↓\nStore Segments + Manifest in S3\n    ↓\nUpdate VideoMetadata\n(with Manifest URL)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dCPGZCcdjoMvLfClsI2kB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2842.0524660084184,
      "y": 8573.764993117107,
      "width": 3687.177490234375,
      "height": 2242.4248549763383,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b04",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2014547007,
      "version": 1219,
      "versionNonce": 857444959,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783319183528,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User Requests Video\n    ↓\nClient Fetches VideoMetadata using \nGET /video/:vidoeId -> videoMetadata which has s3 Manifest url's\n    ↓\nClient Gets Manifest URL\n    ↓\nClient Downloads Manifest from S3\n    ↓\nClient Chooses Quality\n    ↓\nClient Downloads Segments from S3\n    ↓\nNetwork Changes?\n    ↓\nDownload Higher/Lower Quality Segments",
      "fontSize": 112.12124274881691,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User Requests Video\n    ↓\nClient Fetches VideoMetadata using \nGET /video/:vidoeId -> videoMetadata which has s3 Manifest url's\n    ↓\nClient Gets Manifest URL\n    ↓\nClient Downloads Manifest from S3\n    ↓\nClient Chooses Quality\n    ↓\nClient Downloads Segments from S3\n    ↓\nNetwork Changes?\n    ↓\nDownload Higher/Lower Quality Segments",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CFygj5vHeF-6uQdjLktQu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -445.04963125320916,
      "y": 9360.300266885086,
      "width": 1412.191883670903,
      "height": 70.00759043590516,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b05",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2015098737,
      "version": 826,
      "versionNonce": 1611197951,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783319189285,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Manifest lists available qualities and segment URLs.",
      "fontSize": 56.00607234872412,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Manifest lists available qualities and segment URLs.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "40d9P8Wy2qNbxf4nW8Y-D",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2161.4417784500056,
      "y": 12582.032959669124,
      "width": 3340.3692670694327,
      "height": 544.0546029083865,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b06",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1306060063,
      "version": 2391,
      "versionNonce": 1056502033,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783317821990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "                 User uploads video to s3 \n                                  |\n                   video Processing Pipeline \n\nffmpeg converts the video into segments(seg1, seg2, seg3, ....)                                                          \n                                   |\nThese segments are transcoded(Transcoding = converting video from one encoding/quality to another.) ",
      "fontSize": 62.17766890381561,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "                 User uploads video to s3 \n                                  |\n                   video Processing Pipeline \n\nffmpeg converts the video into segments(seg1, seg2, seg3, ....)                                                          \n                                   |\nThese segments are transcoded(Transcoding = converting video from one encoding/quality to another.) ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "y2bIZ7gwMY_5NxK6DRkKx",
